# Revisions git blame should skip — large, mechanical, no-author-signal
# commits (bulk reformatting / license-header sweeps). Each line is a full
# 40-char commit SHA.
#
# Enable locally:
#   git config blame.ignoreRevsFile .git-blame-ignore-revs
# GitHub honours this file automatically in its blame view.

